question: Which statement is a description of weather?
candidate_answers: (A) Summers in Tucson are hot and dry. (B) Winters in Flagstaff are cold and snowy. (C) The temperature is 55° F in Winslow today. (D) The Sun will set in Yuma today at 6:45 p.m.
answer: The temperature is 55° F in Winslow today.
label: C
